        <abstract>
            <p>Has not been well.</p>
            <p>Plans a geological trip to Glen Roy in Scotland.</p>
            <p>Thanks WDF for remembering the crossing of animals, CD’s "prime hobby". "I really think some day I shall be able to do something on that most intricate subject species and varieties."</p>
        </abstract>
